nodes.title: This workflow is main memory (CPU) intensive
widgets_values:
**⚠️ Dependency Alert! ⚠️**

This workflow is designed to show how much of a complex workflow can be spread across GPUs while offloading as much as it can to main memory (cpu). 

Since this workflow cannot predict every combination of cuda devices and main memory, you might find your desired model component doesn't fit. At that point, your options are to change to a different (larger) device, load a smaller model, or explore GGUF quantizations of existing models. 

Should you want to explore GGUF quantizations, it requires nodes from the [ComfyUI-GGUF](https://github.com/city96/ComfyUI-GGUF) custom node repository to function correctly, along with swapping out to the GGUF versions of the MultiGPU node(s). Please see the GGUF examples located in the same diretory for further exploration.
